Class Paginator<T>

java.lang.Object
no.ntnu.idatt1005.foodi.view.Paginator<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The type of the items to paginate
public class Paginator<T> extends Object
A class for handling a large list of items, and separating them into chunks.
